  "text": "The Pulumi workflow is simple. Initialize a project. Preview the changes. Apply them. And optionally destroy them. The commands map directly. PulumiEdge creates your project. Pulumi Preview shows planned changes. PulumiUp deploys to AWS. PulumiDestroy tears everything down. And PulumiConfig manages per-environment settings.",
